title: Hurricane Sanjou
lyrics: Shushutto sanjou Shushutto ninja jan Maki-okose yuuki no HARI KEEN Kujikesou ni naru kimochi wo ima egao ni kaeta ra Atarashii hibi wo kakete yuku no sa Mae dake mitsumete Kono ho shi wo mamoru tame ni Uke-tsui de kita himitsu no chikara Mittsu no kokoro wo awaseta ra Shinjita mirai ni ganbaro u Shushutto sanjou Shushutto ninja jan Kakugo kakugo kakugo shiro yo zet tai Shushutto sanjou Shushutto Kyou Go! Go! Moe-agare seigi no HARI KEEN Ninpuu Sentai HARIKEN JAA Kaze ni na re
